                <p>WFB, &ldquo;At Home,&rdquo; to &ldquo;My dear K.&rdquo;: asks
                    forgiveness for not visiting her; promises to visit ad stay with her at least
                    two days, wishes it could be longer &ldquo;but it might not look
                    well&rdquo;; his shoulder wound has nearly healed </p>
            </div1>
